text: Przemysław Lewandowski (born 21 July 1975) is a Polish rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Poland Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Poznań
